<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" charset="text/html UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activation mail - Endless Dev</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222222;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .enail-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Endless Dev Platform</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h2>Hi <%= user.name %>,</h2>
            <p>Thanks for signing up for Endless Dev! We're excited to have you on board. To get started, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p>Please enter the code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes</p>
            <p>If you didn't sign up for Endless Dev, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any question, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:endlessdev2023@gmail.com">Contact Us</a></p>
            

        </div>
</body>
</html>